Label: Study PubMed ID
Datatype: String formatted as valid PubMed ID
Description: The PubMed IDs of the described publication(s) associated with this study.

Label: Study Publication DOI
Description: A Digital Object Identifier (DOI) for that publication (where available).

Label: Study Publication Author List
Description: The list of authors associated with that publication.

Label: Study Publication Title
Description: The title of publication associated with the investigation.

Label: Study Publication Status
Datatype: String, or Ontology Annotation by providing accompanying Term Accession Number and Term Source REF
Description: A term describing the status of that publication (i.e. submitted, in preparation, published).

Label: Study Publication Status Term Accession Number
Description: The accession number from the Term Source associated with the selected term.

Label: Study Publication Status Term Source REF
Description: Identifies the controlled vocabulary or ontology that this term comes from. The Source REF has to match one the Term Source Name declared in the in the Ontology Source Reference section.
